title: Logan's War - Bound By Honor -Chuck Norris, Eddie Cibrian

Movies : Action : DVD Rip : Estonian
Movie Description
When Logan Fallon (Eddie Cibrian) was ten, his prosecutor father invoked the rage of organized crime, and Logan's entire family was executed by a hit man, but Logan avoided death with the help of a psychic sense that warned him of impending danger. Knowing the identity of the murderer, Logan decided not to tell investigators, but instead put into motion a long-term plan for revenge! Growing up with his Uncle Jake (Chuck Norris), Logan learns martial arts and becomes an Army Ranger, and now the uncle and nephew are ready to exact their vengeance!

Credits 
Cast: Chuck Norris, Eddie Cibrian 
Director: Michael Preece
